鯦字的基本解释

鯦
jiù
鲥鱼。

鯦字的汉语字典释义

[①]［jiù］
［《集韻》巨救切，去宥，羣。］
鱼名。也称魱、当魱。即鲥鱼。

鯦字的康熙字典解释

【亥集中】【魚字部】　鯦； 康熙笔画：19； 页码：页1473第09
【唐韻】其久切【集韻】巨九切，?音臼。【說文】當互也。【爾雅·釋魚】鯦，當魱。【註】海魚也。詳前魱字註。又【集韻】巨救切，音舊。義同。又【集韻】徐由切，音囚。魚名。似鯿而大鱗，肥美，多鯁。或作鰽。又【集韻】字秋切，音酋。義同。又【集韻】倚亥切，音欸。叔鮪也。

鯦字的源字形

字源演变：

小篆楷体

字形对比：

中国大陆宋体台湾细明体香港明体韩国明朝体
鯦字的起名意思

暂无。

Kangxi dictionary interpretation of words
[Hai Collection] [Fish Character Department] 　鯦; Kangxi Strokes: 19; Page Number: Page 1473 Page 09
【Tang Yun】Its long cut 【Ji Yun】has a huge nine-cut, with a sound mortar. [Said the text] When each other also. 【Erya·Shiyu】Grate, be a scorpion. [Note] Marine fish also. Please refer to the previous note. Also 【Jiyun】Great rescue cut, the sound is old. The same meaning. [Ji Yun] Xu Youqie, the prisoner of sound. The name of the fish. It resembles a bream and has large scales, plump, and abundance. Or as 鰽. Also【Jiyun】The word Qiuqie, the sound chieftain. The same meaning. Also [Jiyun] Lean on Haiqie, sound Hey. Uncle Tuna also.
